## Final Notes

**This is a living guide about AI-assisted development, being created with AI-assisted development.**

The irony is intentional. The meta-ness is feature, not bug.

If something in this methodology doesn't work while building this documentation, that's a sign to revise the methodology.

**Trust the process. It works.**

